 Non-structured magic was a lot rarer in the past, both due to the more
 primitive shaping instruction at that time and because magical bloodlines used
 to be smaller and less sophisticated.
 The marker, and even the time loop itself, may have been built with a set of
 assumptions that were simply not valid today as they once had been.
 And whoever had activated the Sovereign Gate either couldn't or wouldn't
 update it to take modern circumstances into account.

\end_layout

